snippet: Portland Fire and Rescue says a girl in her early teens sustained life-threatening injuries when she fell more than 40 feet off the cliffs at a popular hiking and climbing spot....

headline.print_headline: Teen Badly Injured in 40-Foot Fall From Cliffs
headline.main: Teen Badly Injured in 40-Foot Fall From Cliffs

lead_paragraph: Portland Fire and Rescue says a girl in her early teens sustained life-threatening injuries when she fell more than 40 feet off the cliffs at a popular hiking and climbing spot.
